    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but i really dont have time to go to a clinic right now, work is crazy. if it is just conjunctivitis, i've heard that getting some antibiotic drops from the pharmacy without a prescription is fine for a few days to see if it clears up. wouldn't that be okay to try first before making a whole thing out of it?",
